title: Ketanji Brown Jackson [TEASER]
itunes:title: Ketanji Brown Jackson [TEASER]
description:
The Supreme Court term begins next week and for the first time in American history, a Black woman will sit among the justices. Here's everything you need to know about Justice Ketanji Brown Jackson's background, judicial philosophy, and approach to haters.


The full version of this premium episode is available exclusively to our Patreon supporters. To join, visit www.patreon.com/fivefourpod


Follow Peter (@The_Law_Boy), Rhiannon (@AywaRhiannon) and Michael (@_FleerUltra) on Twitter.
